            <div class="title">
                Destroyers, Corfu (Mine Explosions)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1946-10-23/debates/d13e9a8f-3e42-4123-bbd4-9e85c2f2ffb2/ForeignAffairs" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
